# 🏦 Loan Risk Prediction System

A production-ready machine learning system that predicts loan approval outcomes using applicant financial and personal data. Built with Python, Scikit-learn, FastAPI, and Docker.

---

## 🚀 Live Demo

```bash
docker pull loan-api
docker run -p 8000:8000 loan-api
```

Then open: `http://localhost:8000/docs`

---

## 📌 Project Overview

Financial institutions face significant risk when approving loans without proper risk assessment. This system provides an intelligent, API-driven tool that analyzes applicant features and predicts loan approval probability — helping banks reduce default risk and improve decision-making efficiency.

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Language | Python 3.11 |
| ML Framework | Scikit-learn |
| API | FastAPI |
| Containerization | Docker |
| Data Processing | Pandas, NumPy |
| Serialization | Joblib |

---

## 📊 Model Performance

| Model | Training AUC | Testing AUC |
|---|---|---|
| Logistic Regression ✅ | 0.699 | **0.875** |
| Decision Tree | 1.000 | 0.698 |
| KNN | 0.622 | 0.517 |

**Selected model:** Logistic Regression — best generalization with 87.5% AUC on test set.

Final accuracy on test set: **93.3%**

